title: No. 9 Tech wins 7-6 thriller over No. 3 OSU - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: No. 9 Tech wins 7-6 thriller over No. 3 OSU - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: STILLWATER, Okla. – The Top 10 billing lived up to the hype. In a contest that went down to the wire, No. 9 Texas Tech outlasted No. 3 Oklahoma State, 7-6, Friday night at O'Brate Stadium to kick off a crucial Big 12 series between two teams vying for the conference crown.
